CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 17, 1960, pg. A1D reads: "Partying - This happy group enjoys itself at the Loendi Club at a party given last week by bandleader Walt Harper. Left to right: Mr. and Mrs. Ron Jefferson, drummer with the Les McCann Trio, now appearing at the Crawford Grill Al Drears, drummer with Dizzy Gillespie Ray Moskie, drummer with the Billy Taylor Trio; Doug Watkins, bassist with Billy Taylor's group, and Mr. and Mrs. Les McCann (he's currently appearing at Crawford Grill) - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Mrs. Jefferson, Ron Jefferson, Al Drears, Ray Moskie, Alberta Thompson, Doug Watkins, Mrs. McCann, and Les McCann, seated on porch of Loendi Club
